{"word":"νοέω","slug":"νοέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>νοέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νοῦς\">νοῦς</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘grasp with mind/heart’, <b>understand <a href='B:470 15:17'>Mt 15:17</a>; <a href='B:470 16:9'>16:9</a>, <a href='B:470 16:11'>11</a>; <a href='B:480 7:18'>Mk 7:18</a>; <a href='B:480 8:17'>8:17</a>; <a href='B:500 12:40'>J 12:40</a>; <a href='B:520 1:20'>Ro 1:20</a>; <a href='B:560 3:4'>Eph 3:4</a>; <a href='B:610 1:7'>1 Ti 1:7</a>; <a href='B:650 11:3'>Hb 11:3</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘give thought to’, <b>think (about), ponder <a href='B:620 2:7'>2 Ti 2:7</a>; think of <a href='B:560 3:20'>Eph 3:20</a>.</b> In a special alert to the (public?) reader<b> <a href='B:470 24:15'>Mt 24:15</a>; <a href='B:480 13:14'>Mk 13:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:νίψαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:νόημα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}